Query/manipulate operational parameters.
.Ar paramspec
has the following format:
.Pp
.Bd -unfilled -offset 3n
.Sm off
.Oo Ar thread-name Ns Li .\& Oc Ar param
.Op Oo Li +- Oc Li = Ar value
.Sm on
.Ed
