.Sx Thread Specification
for details on specifying
.Ar thread-name .
The default behavior is to apply the operation to all applicable threads.
.Pp
.Ar param
may be one of the following:
.Bl -tag -width 1n -offset 3n
.It Cm fuse.debug
.Tn FUSE
debug messages.
.It Cm fuse.version
